title: Alison Roman's Quick and Easy Ragù | NYT Cooking
description:
Alison Roman is back with a quick and easy lamb ragù. It's a simple sauce made mostly with pantry staples. It's delicious and unapologetically lamb-forward. If you prefer, you could use pork, beef or a mix of all three. Get the recipe: http://nyti.ms/2lSuB7d
